View.Name: WorkerStatus
View.CheckCode:
DefineVariables DEFINE ERHMS NETOBJECT "ERHMS Info Manager.Integration" End-DefineVariables
Field WorkerInfo_LookUpId Click ASSIGN WorkerInfo_GlobalRecordId = ERHMS.LookUpWorkerId(WorkerInfo_FirstName, WorkerInfo_LastName, WorkerInfo_GlobalRecordId) End-Click End-Field

Field.Name: Instructions
Field.PromptText: Include all work performed on this incident since the worker's previous report. If this is the worker's first report for this incident, include all work performed since the beginning of deployment.

Field.Name: WorkHours
Field.PromptText: How many hours of work were performed?

Field.Name: WorkLocations
Field.PromptText: Where did this work take place?

Field.Name: Exposed
Field.PromptText: Was the worker exposed to any hazards?

Field.Name: ExposureType
Field.PromptText: What hazards was the worker exposed to?

Field.Name: WorePPE
Field.PromptText: Did the worker wear personal protective equipment (PPE)?

Field.Name: WornPPEType
Field.PromptText: What PPE did the worker wear?

Field.Name: EyeProtection
Field.PromptText: Eye protection (safety glasses, goggles, face shield, visor, etc.)

Field.Name: SkinProtection
Field.PromptText: Skin protection (sunscreen, hat, long sleeves, etc.)

Field.Name: RespiratorType
Field.PromptText: Type of respirator worn, if any:

Field.Name: Injured
Field.PromptText: Did the worker experience any injuries or illnesses?

Field.Name: InjuryType
Field.PromptText: What injuries/illnesses did the worker experience?
